# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required in any non-local environment. Render / Supabase / Neon all hand out
# `postgresql://...` URLs by default — `_ensure_db_url()` in db/connection.py
# auto-fixes the scheme to `postgresql+asyncpg://`, so this value is fine as-is.
# For free-tier stability, use the Supabase **pooler** hostname on port 6543
# (transaction-mode pooler), not the direct connection on 5432.
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.xxxx:[PASSWORD]@aws-0-us-east-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres

# ── Downstream API endpoints ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
CF_API_BASE=https://codeforces.com/api
LC_GRAPHQL_URL=https://leetcode.com/graphql

# ── Model weights ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Defaults to ./weights/graph_dkt.pt. File is gitignored; if missing, the
# lifespan falls back to rule-based mastery (`model_used: "rule_based"`).
MODEL_WEIGHTS_PATH=./weights/graph_dkt.pt

# ── CORS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated list of allowed frontend origins. Lowercased on read; the
# Vercel production URL is required, localhost is for `npm run dev`.
FRONTEND_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,https://cp-coach.vercel.app

# ── Auth (intentionally NOT set for the public site) ─────────────────────────
# See backend/auth.py for the full deployment model. For the public research
# demo at https://cp-coach.vercel.app, leave CP_API_SECRET UNSET — the rate
# limiter is the only abuse mitigation. For non-public deployments, set this
# to a strong random value and arrange for a server-side proxy to sign
# requests with `Authorization: HMAC <sig>` + `X-Timestamp: <unix-ts>` headers.
# CP_API_SECRET=
